snippet.title: Guns, Beats n' Dragons - Full playthrough [SPOILER]
snippet.description:
Playthrough of Guns, Beats n' Dragons, a game I made for the Lowrezjam (I'm using the mouse instead of the arrows, I think it's a bit easier).

Game can be played on Gamejolt : http://gamejolt.com/games/arcade/guns-beats-n-dragons/27444/

All copyrights and credits to Oddly Shaped Pixels.
